2. ATTRIBUTION: If this project significantly informs the structure or design of your own work, you must provide a clear "Inspired by" credit to "Fascinating Pistachio" with a link to the original Florendex repository.
3. RESTRICTIONS: You may NOT replicate the Florendex codebase, content, or visual likeness in its entirety. Redistribution, commercial use, or submission of this code (in whole or in part) as your own academic work is strictly prohibited.

